ns1:contractData.ns1:descriptionOfContractRequirement:
THE PURPOSE OF THIS MODIFICATION IS TO REFLECT THE FOLLOWING CHANGES:
1. ADDS INDIVIDUAL CASE BASIS (ICB) CUSTOM ACCESS ARRANGEMENT (CAA), AS DESCRIBED IN SUBMITTAL AU3615.01E;
2. ADDS CSDES ICB PRICING, AS DESCRIBED IN SUBMITTAL AU3685.01E;
3. LOWERS ONE CSDES PRICE, REDUCING THE EXISTING ICB PRICE AND CHANGING THE PRICING VOLUME, AS DESCRIBED IN SUBMITTAL AU3689.01P;
4. REDUCES A PREVIOUSLY AWARDED PRICE, REMOVING THE 7% FEE AND CHANGING THE PRICING VOLUME FOR DOMESTIC BROADBAND ETHERNET ACCESS BY NSC (MRC) - REDUCE DOMESTIC BROADBAND ETHERNET ACCESS BY NSC (MRC) PRICE, AS DESCRIBED IN SUBMITTAL AU3673.01P;
5. REDUCES A PREVIOUSLY AWARDED PRICE, AND PROPOSED CHANGES TO THE PRICING VOLUME OF DOMESTIC BROADBAND ETHERNET ACCESS BY NSC (MRC) - REDUCE DOMESTIC BROADBAND ETHERNET ACCESS BY NSC (MRC) PRICE, AS DESCRIBED IN SUBMITTAL AU3688.01P.
6. .THE TOTAL ESTIMATED DOLLAR VALUE OF THE CONTRACT IS UNCHANGED BY THIS MODIFICATION.
7. ALL SUBMITTALS BEING ADDED TO THE CONTRACT ARE EXCLUSIVE OF COVER LETTERS AND ANY SUPPORTING DOCUMENTATION SUBMITTED TO THE NHC.

